_______________________________________________________________________________
"Ectoplasmic Form"
	It allows the psionicist to leave his or her own body and roam
	the land as an insubstantial phantom.  The phantom is entirely
	invulnerable to attack and cannot damage any monsters or pick
	any items up.  While they are in ectoplasmic form psionicists'
	own bodies will lie dormant, unable to be given any commands.
        To end this power, type 'end'.
 
SP Cost:  75		Guild Level:  5		Potential Points:  2
 
Command:  eform
